      <title>QMK Firmware in M1</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/post/2023/04/02/qmk-firmware-in-m1/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Apr 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/post/2023/04/02/qmk-firmware-in-m1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Running &lt;code&gt;./util/qmk_install.sh&lt;/code&gt; won&amp;rsquo;t work. You need rosetta-enabled terminal session then run these command below:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ arch -x86_64 /bin/bash -c &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ arch -x86_64 /usr/local/bin/brew install qmk/qmk/qmk&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;After that, &lt;code&gt;qmk&lt;/code&gt; is accessible from anywhere, even from non-rosetta terminal session.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/herpiko/unk&#34;&gt;UNK&lt;/a&gt; after being flashed directly from a M1 computer:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/images/2023-04-02-unk.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;UNK&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Happy hacking!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
